Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:53.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最深最远的宇宙尽头依旧想你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:59.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将心愿交付于万千流星播撒四方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论天边（抑或眼前）渴望与你相见（渴望与你相见）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好似就要传达给你（却无法传达） 总是红着双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你我（总有一天）化作繁星（逐渐默淡）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:10.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运 宿命 是谁的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:14.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿将一切倾注于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激烈 炸裂 強烈 破裂 爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:18.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛-烈！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:23.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作满天星斗中的一颗（化作繁星）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:28.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的爱恒久不灭（如此珍视）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这思念（向着爱）烈烈燃烧（燃烧着）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:39.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷如炽热而耀眼的天蝎之星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我为爱而生）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:46.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕未来还有几亿光年（这思念亦永不消逝）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:50.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亦不在乎 只因喜欢你（没错 如此喜欢）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的祈愿（终点） 永不消逝（直到永远）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:01.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁星的絮语将永远守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛-烈！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:53.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙の果ての果てでも　君のこと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:59.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾多の流れ星で　願いを撒き散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くて(近くて)会いたくて(会いたくて)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,届きそうで(届かなくて)いつだって涙目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰だって（いつかは）星となり(消えていく)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:10.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運命　宿命　誰のせい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:14.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕のすべて捧げるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激烈 炸裂 強烈 破裂 爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:18.93,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もーれつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:23.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星屑のクズと成りて(星となり)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:28.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君に恋し続けよう(哀切に？大切に？)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思いは（愛に）燃えてる(燃える)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:39.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤く赤く光るアンタレスのように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（どいつも いつまでも）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:46.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何億光年先だって(思いは消えない)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:50.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構わない　そう、好きだから(大好きだから)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願いは(終わり)　消えない(ずっと)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:01.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星のこどで君を守り続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もーれつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(426,440)}transponder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射机应答器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于在宇宙航行飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是确认彼此存在的一种发信装置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船名 船籍 现在位置及行进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(256,440)}transponder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射机应答器的信息既是人的意识 也是目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船员通过对船体的熟知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寂静的宇宙空间也变为金色的汪洋大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下的这片宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大航海时代的余韵依然悠长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想稍微更改一下飞行计划
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来会是一个漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照最初计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛塔二世本应沿着从τ星将围绕砂赤星的外侧轨道行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得应该改变航向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽早进入沿着砂赤星太阳一侧的轨道比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来轨道的飞行时间也能节省不少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行计划也可以变得绰绰有余
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到中转站时间也能稍微提前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变更轨道的原因不只是为了缩短时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明一下其它理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以限制敌人的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰即将进入砂赤星的重力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂赤星的周边宇惑在雷达的可观测范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止没发现任何打算对我们出手的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果敌人盯上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至今还没有现身的话 只有一个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他们隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏在…在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在位置来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛塔二世的雷达无法捕捉到区域有两处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么是砂赤星的另一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么是由于辐射过强而导致雷达失灵的太阳内部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我投第一种一票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也投砂赤星的另一侧一票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量获得靠近太阳的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是空中战的入门要领
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正附近也没有船只会受到我们的牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴已提出的飞行计划的不同之处也在误差范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于飞行计划变更的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最接近砂赤星的时间将不再是第四天的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是第三天的午夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老师休息时间开始战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会那么顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方有可能直到天亮才行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是这样的话我们也能离开砂赤星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量吸收太阳光 以提高航行速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最坏的情况 如果什么也没有发生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那就当做这一切都是我的胡思乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡思乱想得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家 今晚就按计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时联络之后 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者接近砂赤星时将有可能最危险的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时联络隔1小时一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达到砂赤星最近点的时间在其5分钟之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我认为这一次的定时联络结束后就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来发送定时联络
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告新的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就像以往一样 报告无异常可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是应该加一句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正准备兴身份不明的敌舰开战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托像往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次的定时联络也应该报告无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被他们发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认通路上没有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能拦截船内的监视器的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会有任何人看见美女船医夜袭船长室的现场画面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你省省吧 我好歹也是有妇之夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是熄灯时间了 大家还都聚集在舰桥里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备好了最低限度的对策
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医务室和米莎的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的监视器也从一开始就切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是当有紧急呼叫时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须切记要装出一副熟睡的摸样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急呼叫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有必要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉香大小姐的反映总是很快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事态恶化到需要我帮助之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就会联络我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你很信任她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也看到她的帆船的模拟飞行训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快速的反映和出众的决意之心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经通过超光速回线将定时联络的定型文本发送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就将同过砂赤星的最近点坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果确实如大小姐所想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人应该差不多向我们发起电子战了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效范围内充满了噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 这就是真正的电子干扰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴军方网站教科书上的反应一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断发送干扰电波 这不过是基础中基础
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们都是门外汉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好对方用的都是初级手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实话 就算现在他们打算来扰乱我们视线也没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这一带的宙惑中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怕闭着眼睛 也不用担心会撞上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算无法使用雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借太阳光重力也能判断方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以依靠仪器航行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超光速回线向管制局发送报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果开通超光速回线 正中敌人的下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(436,440)}time-lag
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被敌人夺走了无延时超光速线路的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们的电子兵器不会那么轻易就被敌人夺取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了 通常线路已确认遭到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时攻击雷达和通讯不就好了 该说他们老实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人这样做才能让我们放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我们这里容易处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照计划那样先当做是故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达的画面设定 改变周波数之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就装作在做这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请从容不迫地应对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的设定是安排两人一组担任值班任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要太过匆忙的应对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我快我也快不了 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统检查 天线已连接 确认雷达无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是重启了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常路线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方进入了隔离区域内的一个的备份系统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们以为这里是奥黛塔二世的系统 在在全力攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时采取了严密的对抗手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(410,440)}defaulf-securitl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过预设安全系统也是很脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次因为事先准备了对抗手段才能从容不迫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们不加注意不知什么时候就会被对方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们的控制权从外部被对方夺走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说是我们的航行方向 就连生命维持系统系统也只能任由对方摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先把电子兵器设定成自动交战模式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是不是更容易想出对策？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对方是之前在中转站攻击我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在自动应答时 我们就已经交过手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的方法不会秦效第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕对方也准备了对抗手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好反而会被对方击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那过去的电子战是怎样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是过去还是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最关键的还是人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防范系统的突破和量子密码演算都可以交给系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从哪里进行攻击 利用什么夺取控制权
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须有人在一开始下达指示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一失败之后该如何应对 也需要人来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动应答无法完成的攻击必须靠手动操作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处在那种情况下的领导者将决定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还挺原始的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备份系统50%已被夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我打算重启雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对方发来干扰电波 现在重启也是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知对方何时会切断干扰电波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候 就算雷达只有一瞬间无法使用也相当可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请切断雷达波的发信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对方认为是我们觉得雷达故障想要重启
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只切断发信的话 很快就能复原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方法不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请切断雷达发信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 切断雷达发信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他需要准备的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备停船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛塔二世的全部系统都正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行系统 无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主机副机均正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输出功率稳步增长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帆船系统 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桅杆 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辐射 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常线路系统 外部攻击仍在持续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超光速通信待命中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子战程序 当然准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁船内所有隔舱 好歹也是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知道会发生什么 先把力所能及的事做好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁船内所有隔舱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备份系统100%被夺取了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部的通常通信被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方肯定以为攻占我们的系统 很快就会现身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在确认指命发来之前 先打开雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达发信 重启
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂赤星方向 一艘位于本船后方宇宙舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(346,440)}transponder
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射机应答器正在发射信号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(406,440)}kilia  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(526,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船籍为西基里亚船 闪电11
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然没有继续发起电子攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为对方认为完全掌握了我方控制权而松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(346,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电11发来紧急电报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(454,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自 闪电11
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致奥黛塔二世船长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰的控制权目前已归我舰管理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻投降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明发的是正式书文却不自报家门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们完全被小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先不要答复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到雷达干扰后还过多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的船目前正在夜间航行之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长答复得过快会显得很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们设定是遭到了奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们这是在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了确认是否夺取这艘船的控制权
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便搜查内部监视器影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我们在制造备份系统时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经连接了程序库管理程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方看到的只是空无一人的船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是两个没事可做的值班人员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算拉响我们船内警报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们看来我们是一群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被攻占也丝毫末察觉到愚蠢女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以亲切地拉响警报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来通知我们船上发生紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 响了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来该熟睡的愚蠢女高中生就全被吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个迷迷糊糊的巡航部部长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也可以给对方一个含糊不清的答复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线路设定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用超光速回线连接上了对方中枢系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是电子战 但对方的防范系统也太脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给出答复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发送方 奥黛塔二世船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇女子学园巡航部部长 杰妮·德里特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(380,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致闪电11船长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正文 你们这群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正文 你们这群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要我再说一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…副部长…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在部长发送信息的同时 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(436,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船将展开对闪电11的电子攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对雷达和通信波发射干扰电波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香具山光好 谁家晾素衣 夏风吹袖满 不必唤春归
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}注：语出百人一首之二持统天皇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回信成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}注：语出百人一首之80待贤门院堀河 部长这里进行诙谐修改
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(426,440)}「曾言心不变 我自愿迟迟 今夜干扰波 忧思君可知」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时对对方的通讯线路和超光速通讯线路入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方真不愧是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方 线路切断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们的电子战系统也是琳琅满目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 敌人的干扰电波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太慢了 而且太弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这种程度的话 我们只要加大输出功率即可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝宇宙中 奥黛塔二世 且闻此花香 前路漫漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}注：这应该是部长原创
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说输出功率 这家伙可是战舰级别的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 被我们控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击他们引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留通信的动力即可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(424,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急停止闪电11主机设备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一 把他们的备用的副引擎也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 机器出故障？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴敌舰的系统连接突然之间消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(336,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴闪电11的通信线路被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被切断的不是线路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(296,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电11那群家伙关闭电脑电源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对方切断了电源 我们的胜利也化作泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡影？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量波接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量波是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想对方正用激光炮瞄准着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是关闭电脑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要主动力还能运转 他们就可以为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才趁被阻止之前关闭电脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有雷达波 也没有通信回线应答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船是怎么瞄准我们的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有像样点的炮塔 都应该装备了光学渺准器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学瞄准器？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么 没有雷达还怎么进行远距离射击？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(466,440)}targer-scope
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己肉眼盯瞄准器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再将准心对准目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用肉眼瞄准？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 比刚才更近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶然吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说每次都随时进行修正精度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 难道就任由他们攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船既没有激光炮也没有防护盾都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(206,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电11为了进行远距离精密射击无法随意移动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话我们还不如利用通常推进来加速 快点逃离…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下的状况 如果点燃了引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是光学瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连红外线探测器也能摸出我们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样我们就无法反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能查出敌舰的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比刚才更近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高频率雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(336,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对目标闪电11现在位置进行精密观测
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:18:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在我们后方40万公里处 总宽度30米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合我的调整 桅杆已经全部运转
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将通过率变成0的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(300,440)}solar-sail
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳帆就能100%反射太阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后调整它 使其在奥黛塔二世的背面成为焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次射击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(374,440)}Lighting 11
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电11的动向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无动向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是惯性航行 反应无变化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 红外线反应增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是照到他们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用太阳光烤焦他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要 只要让他们用不了光学瞄准器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是追过来了？还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是发现了新目标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新目标？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还有一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来援军到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是怎么有两艘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(366,440)}transponder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射机应答器正在运作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后方来的一艘是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海贼船弁天丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一艘是 海贼船巴巴罗萨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我家的船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很庆幸来看下任船长候补是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我重新做一下自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙海贼船巴巴罗萨号船长栗原见城女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栗原千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的船和巴巴罗萨都一点不手软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系军也登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是星系军第六护卫舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认航行中的奥黛塔二世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有需要我们帮助的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是奥黛塔二世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时没有需要帮助的地方 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝航行愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始七舰之「白鸟号」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还完全绰绰有余呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成为船长的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为 宇宙海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你 一切平安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:11.49,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(486,254)\fad(750,1000)}航线 5
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:11.49,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,1000)\fs24\pos(536,394)\c&HF9F2FD&}茉莉香、下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本该愉快的暑假变成了连日辛苦训练
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周遭的期望 自身的紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在种种思绪的交织之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次的「海贼营业」开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 暴力宇宙海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉香 第一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:23:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H4A4A4A&\be5\pos(326,371)}茉莉香、第一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:12.30,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,(C.M.S. C.M.A. O.P.R. Into the space)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:12.30,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,(C.M.S. C.M.A. O.P.R. Into the space)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:17.95,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,(M.C.Z. Overall O.I.E. What's goin' on？)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:17.95,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,(M.C.Z. Overall O.I.E. What's goin' on？)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:21.06,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,ようこそ　栄光　突破口　いま飛びだすんだ Let's Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:21.06,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到光荣的突破口 现在开始飞跃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.33,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,無限の次元へ疾走　さあ速攻で超えてこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.33,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,向着无限次元狂奔 以速攻来超越吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:27.53,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,時こえ知るべき歴史　あるべき未来へ向かい Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:27.53,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,穿越时空 需知的历史 向应有的未来飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:30.65,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡あきらめたら化石　決断は自分の選んだベスト
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:30.65,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,若放弃奇迹便为化石 以自己选择的最佳做决断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:39.42,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,私の中に 知らない私が 隠れているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:39.42,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,在我心中 隐藏着未知的我
